name: Conjuring
description:
Here's a bit of life advice that I think will help out a lot of people.

"In life, you have to work hard to conjure up opportunities but when they turn up remember to boot them away and not take them because it will probably mean more work and that"

hand drawm animation, 1650 × 1650px, 8 seconds, twitter @james_clapham, IG @jamesclaphamillustration
